    {
      "rule": "Avoid generic or empty statements. Do not publish vague, clichéd, or low-value claims (e.g. “cutting-edge”, “powerful”, “we are cloud”). Every statement must convey meaningful, differentiated information.",
      "ruleStrength": "SHOULD",
      "status": "Proposal",
      "type": "Design principle",
